ure Production Company\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Hollywood Music in Media Awards]]\n| November 16, 2017\n| Best Original Score \u2013 Sci-Fi/Fantasy/Horror Film\n| [[Marco Beltrami]]\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.shootonline.com/spw/hollywood-music-media-awards-announces-nominees-film-tv-video-game-music|title=Hollywood Music in Media Awards Announces Nominees in Film, TV, & Video Game Music|author=Shoot Editors |work=[[Shoot (advertising magazine)|Shoot]]|date=October 24, 2017|accessdate=December 4, 2017}}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/hollywood-music-media-awards-full-winners-list-1057748/item/original-score-animated-film-1057703|title=Hollywood Music in Media Awards: Full Winners List|author=The Hollywood Reporter Editors |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=November 17, 2017|accessdate=December 4, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[Houston Film Critics Society]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Houston Film Critics Society Awards 2017|January 6, 2018]]\n| [[Houston Film Critics Society Award for Best Picture|Best Picture]]\n| ''Logan''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.awardsdaily.com/2017/12/12/houston-film-critics-release-nominations/|title=Houston Film Critics Release Nominations|last=Stone|first=Sasha|work=Awards Daily|date=December 12, 2017|accessdate=December 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Houston Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actor|Best Supporting Actor]]\n| Patrick Stewart\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Houston Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actress|Best Supporting Actress]]\n| Dafne Keen\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"5\"| [[IGN|IGN Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"5\"| December 19, 2017\n| Movie of the Year\n| ''Logan''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"5\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2017-awards/Movie_of_the_Year|title=BEST OF 2017 NOMINEES |author=IGN Editors |work=[[IGN Awards]]|date=December 4, 2017|accessdate=December 5, 2